Description: This github repository serves as a template for a short-form workshop, lesson, or course to be shared in the form of a pkgdown website with slides rendered by xaringan. This description text for the package and lesson should be written in `README.Rmd`, which, when knit, will then update the package's `DESCRIPTION` file.
